data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Lovely maintenance free 4 bed 3 bath townhome in Colonial Pines! This is an end unit flooded with natural light. The first floor features 2 bedrooms each with their own ensuite, living room with fireplace, dining room, kitchen, and laundry. Upstairs are 2 additional bedrooms, full bath, and a walk-in attic. New roof in 2016 and new HVAC in 2019. Yard maintenance included in your monthly HOA! Schedule your showing today, this beautiful home won't last long.
